Description.de: Stadtwege und Parkanlagen werden für eine zeitgemäße gesundheitsfördernde Nutzung von Seiten der Meraner BürgerInnen herangezogen und in Zusammenarbeit mit Medizinern neu bestimmt und gestaltet.
Description.en: Merano citizens are rediscovering urban routes and parks through a contemporary lens, prioritizing health and wellness. Together with medical professionals and experts, they are reshaping and revitalizing these spaces.
Description.it: Percorsi all’interno del tessuto urbano e parchi vengono riscoperti in chiave moderna e salutista da parte delle cittadine e dei cittadini di Merano e ridefiniti e riallestiti in collaborazione con medici ed esperti.

Description.de: Das Event …stellt in den Fokus, wofür Südtirol steht (z.B. kultureller/historischer Bezug, hochwertige Kulinarik, authentische Inhalte, gesunde Bewegung/Sport). …verfügt über eine professionelle Organisation und Kommunikation in mind. 3 Sprachen.  …ist so begehrlich, dass sich eine längere Anreise lohnt.
Description.en: The event… …showcases what makes South Tyrol unique (from its authenticity, rich traditions and history to its passion for sports and healthy living, and its renowned food and wine excellence. …is professionally organized and communicated in at least three languages. …this event is so captivating that it's worth the trip.
Description.it: L'evento ...mette in risalto ciò che rende unico l'Alto Adige (come le tradizioni e la storia, lo sport e l’ attività fisica, l'autenticità e l'eccellenza enogastronomica). ...dispone di organizzazione e comunicazione professionale in almeno 3 lingue. ...è un’esperienza così affascinante da valere un lungo viaggio.

Description.de: Bereits der Architekt Le Corbusier wusste: Die Dolomiten in Südtirol sind das schönste Bauwerk der Welt. Tatsächlich wurden die Dolomiten „erbaut“. Die Berge bestehen aus versteinerten Algen- und Korallenriffen. 250 Millionen Jahre lang wuchsen sie im warmen Tethysmeer und als dieses absank, stiegen die Dolomiten weiß, majestätisch und bizarr auf, als „bleiche Berge“, die anders waren als alle Berge ringsum.
Description.en: Born as coral reefs 250 million years ago, today they soar skywards proud and confident as white towers of rock.
Description.it: La genesi delle Dolomiti vanta 250 milioni di anni di storia: nacquero come barriera corallina e oggi si ergono verso il cielo come bianche torri di roccia. Proprio per questo le Dolomiti sono Patrimonio Mondiale UNESCO. Prima di passare delle belle vacanze attive o di relax in Alto Adige, assicuratevi di sapere e di conoscerne la storia delle Dolomiti, il Patrimonio Mondiale UNESCO.

Description.cs: There’s nothing better than to doze off and dream sweet dreams  under  the sun on the Ritten. However, sport  activities are hard to resist. Families simply love the soft and spacious skiing slopes of the Rittner Horn, hikers and cross-country skiers praise the idyllic winter wonderland, and ice skaters f lock to the fastest outdoor track in the world. Winter paradise for everyone.
Description.de: Es gibt kaum etwas Schöneres, als auf dem Ritten in der Sonne zu träumen, doch die sportlichen Verlockungen sind groß. Familien und Einsteiger lieben die sanften, breiten Pisten am Rittner Horn, Wanderer und Langläufer schwärmen von der idyllischen Winterlandschaft und dem wunderbarem Blick auf die Dolomiten, Eisläufer treibt es zur schnellsten Freiluftbahn der Welt oder auf den See. Ein Wintertraum für jeden.
Description.en: There’s nothing better than to doze off and dream sweet dreams  under  the sun on the Ritten. However, sport  activities are hard to resist. Families simply love the soft and spacious skiing slopes of the Rittner Horn, hikers and cross-country skiers praise the idyllic winter wonderland, and ice skaters f lock to the fastest outdoor track in the world. Winter paradise for everyone.

Families simply love the soft and spacious skiing slopes of the Rittner Horn, hikers and cross-country skiers praise the idyllic winter wonderland, and ice skaters f lock to the fastest outdoor track in the world. Winter paradise for everyone.
Description.it: Sognare sul Renon accarezzati dai raggi del sole è la cosa  più bella del mondo, resa ancor più speciale dalle numerose attività sportive offerte. Le famiglie apprezzano le dolci e ampie discese sul Corno del Renon, gli appassionati di escursioni e sci di fondo adorano l’idilliaco paesaggio innevato e il panorama mozzafiato panorama sulle Dolomiti, mentre gli amanti del pattinaggio su ghiaccio restano affascinati dalla pista all’aperto più veloce del mondo o sul lago. Qui, tutti possono realizzare i loro sogni invernali.

Description.cs: Slow Food Travel is a Slow Food project that aims to develop and promote a sustainable travel experience. Slow Food Travel is therefore a new travel model made up of meetings and exchanges with farmers and artisans who, together with the cooks who cook their products, become narrators and guides of their territories.
Description.de: Slow Food Travel ist ein Projekt von Slow Food, das darauf abzielt, ein nachhaltiges Reiseerlebnis zu entwickeln. Es handelt sich also um ein neues Reisemodell von Slow Food, das aus Begegnungen und dem Austausch mit Landwirten und Handwerkern besteht, die zusammen mit den Köchen, die ihre Produkte verarbeiten, die Geschichten ihrer lokalen Gebiete und der lokalen Traditionen erzählen.
Description.en: Slow Food Travel is a Slow Food project that aims to develop and promote a sustainable travel experience. Slow Food Travel is therefore a new travel model made up of meetings and exchanges with farmers and artisans who, together with the cooks who cook their products, become narrators and guides of their territories.
Description.fr: Slow Food Travel is a Slow Food project that aims to develop and promote a sustainable travel experience. Slow Food Travel is therefore a new travel model made up of meetings and exchanges with farmers and artisans who, together with the cooks who cook their products, become narrators and guides of their territories.
Description.it: Slow Food Travel è un progetto di Slow Food che ha come obiettivi lo sviluppo e la promozione di un'esperienza di viaggio sostenibile. Slow Food Travel è quindi un nuovo modello di viaggio fatto di incontri e scambi con agricoltori e artisani che, insieme ai cuochi che cucinano i loro prodotti, si fanno narratori e guide dei loro territori.
Description.nl: Slow Food Travel is a Slow Food project that aims to develop and promote a sustainable travel experience. Slow Food Travel is therefore a new travel model made up of meetings and exchanges with farmers and artisans who, together with the cooks who cook their products, become narrators and guides of their territories.

Description.cs: With the "Autumn Special" package we hope to make your stay even more enjoyable and unforgettable. Embark on guided hikes and mtb-tours to see the animals that live at high altitudes, visit the museums of mountain and Ladin culture, or feel an adrenaline rush as you descend the longest zipline in Europe! San Vigilio in autumn, an unforgettable experience.
Description.de: Mit dem Herbstangebot "Autumn Special" möchten wir Ihren Aufenthalt unvergesslich machen. Begeben Sie sich auf geführte Wanderungen und MTB Touren, besuchen Sie die Museen der Berg- und ladinischen Kultur oder spüren Sie den Adrenalinstoß, wenn Sie die längste Zipline Europas benutzen! San Vigilio Dolomites im Herbst, ein unvergessliches Erlebnis.
Description.en: With the "Autumn Special" package we hope to make your stay even more enjoyable and unforgettable. Embark on guided hikes and mtb-tours to see the animals that live at high altitudes, visit the museums of mountain and Ladin culture, or feel an adrenaline rush as you descend the longest zipline in Europe! San Vigilio in autumn, an unforgettable experience.
Description.fr: With the "Autumn Special" package we hope to make your stay even more enjoyable and unforgettable. Embark on guided hikes and mtb-tours to see the animals that live at high altitudes, visit the museums of mountain and Ladin culture, or feel an adrenaline rush as you descend the longest zipline in Europe! San Vigilio in autumn, an unforgettable experience.
Description.it: Con il pacchetto "Autumn Special" speriamo di rendere il vostro soggiorno ancora più piacevole e memorabile. Incamminatevi in escursioni guidate per vedere gli animali che vivono ad alta quota, partecipate ai giri guidati in MTB, visitate i musei della montagna e della cultura ladina, o sentite una scarica di adrenalina scendendo lungo la zipline più lunga d'Europa! San Vigilio in autunno, un'esperienza indimenticabile.
Description.nl: With the "Autumn Special" package we hope to make your stay even more enjoyable and unforgettable. Embark on guided hikes and mtb-tours to see the animals that live at high altitudes, visit the museums of mountain and Ladin culture, or feel an adrenaline rush as you descend the longest zipline in Europe!
